908, and: La Tribuna di Portchester, dic. 1908. Suspended with ott. 24, 1908 issue: resumed with nov. 25, 1908 issue. Also issued on microfilm from Connecticut State Library, Hartford, CT. In Italian, 1906-1908. In Italian and English, apr. 29-magg. 5, 1906, nov.-dic. 1908. Description based on: Anno I, Num. 1 (3 Marzo 1906); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed May 1, 2019). Latest issue consulted: Anno II, No. 44 (9 Dicembre 1908) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed May 1, 2019)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:47.851Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2019271086/", "image_url": [], "index": 5, "language": ["italian", "english"], "location": ["bridgeport", "new york", "fairfield", "connecticut", "port chester", "united states", "danbury"], "number": ["online resource", "2643-5462", "2019271086", "1099575389", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Tribuna del Port Chester, N.Y.", "Tribuna di Danbury", "Tribuna di Portchester"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "la tribuna del connecticut (bridgeport, conn.) 1906-1908 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 50.939365, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["danbury", "bridgeport", "port chester", "connecticut", "fairfield", "newspapers", "new york (state)", "united states", "italian", "bridgeport (conn.)", "port chester (n.y.)", "italian americans", "danbury (conn.)"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:58:32.070Z", "title": "La tribuna del Connecticut", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2019271086/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://lccn.loc.gov/sn92051386", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn92051386/", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/4699c33a-66e7-571e-a916-ddd1c2169ccc"], "batch": ["ct_clash_ver